	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murray_Head" title="Murray Head">Murray Head</a> as Bob Elkin</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peggy_Ashcroft" title="Peggy Ashcroft">Peggy Ashcroft</a> as Mrs. Greville</li>
	<li><a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tony_Britton" title="Tony Britton">Tony Britton</a> as George Harding</li>
